---
title: Mexican Goodness Bowl with Roasted Squash, Black Beans and Tomato Salad
description: Quinoa is a pseudo-cereal ( a seed which is prepared and consumed like a grain) and is one of a few plant food which can be considered to be a complete protein as it contains all 9 essential amino acids. Forming the base of our delicious Mexican-inspired goodness bowl, quinoa is topped with fresh zingy ingredients like roasted spiced butternut squash, black bean purée, tomato salad and peppery rocket. Hearty and wholesome, this healthy recipe is the perfect thing for an easy mid-week dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mexican-goodness-bowl-8ad6aa88-591b85a8.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/mexican-goodness-bowl-5c11292be3f339588f2bd502-579e80af.pdf
servings: 2
cuisine: Mexican
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
time required: 35 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/mexican-goodness-bowl-5c11292be3f339588f2bd502
nutrition:
  calories: 473 kcal
  fat: 9 g
  saturated fat: 1 g
